<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>InternFlow Sample NDA</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>InternFlow Sample Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA)</h1>
<p><strong>This is a sample Word-compatible NDA for demo/testing only.</strong></p>
<p>This document is not a legal agreement.</p>

<h2>1. Confidential Information</h2>
<p>Confidential Information includes non-public business, technical, product, process,
customer, and operational details shared during internship onboarding and execution.</p>

<h2>2. Non-Disclosure Obligation</h2>
<ul>
<li>Keep Confidential Information strictly confidential.</li>
<li>Use Confidential Information only for authorized internship activities.</li>
<li>Do not disclose Confidential Information to unauthorized third parties.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Permitted Access</h2>
<p>Access is limited to personnel with a need-to-know basis and equivalent confidentiality obligations.</p>

<h2>4. Exclusions</h2>
<ul>
<li>Publicly available information without breach.</li>
<li>Lawfully known information before disclosure.</li>
<li>Independently developed information.</li>
<li>Lawfully received information from a third party.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Term and Retention</h2>
<p>Confidentiality obligations continue after internship completion as required by policy or law.</p>
<p>Upon request, information must be returned or securely deleted, except where retention is legally required.</p>

<h2>6. Signature</h2>
<p>Candidate Name: _______________________</p>
<p>Date: _______________________</p>
<p>Signature: _______________________</p>
</body>
</html>
